## Suggested Commands

```bash
# Create branch
git checkout -b fix/cloudflare-runtime-drift-sla-review-board

# Verify docs after creation
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-runtime-drift-sla.md
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-ownership-review-board.md
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-drift-exception-register.md
cat docs/infra/cloudflare-monthly-governance-evidence.md

# Check no secrets in new files
grep -RInE '(token|secret|password|credential|api[_-]?key)' docs/infra/cloudflare-runtime-drift-sla.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-ownership-review-board.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-drift-exception-register.md \
  docs/infra/cloudflare-monthly-governance-evidence.md || echo "No secrets found"

# Check markdown structure
grep -c "##" docs/infra/cloudflare-runtime-drift-sla.md

# Git status
git diff --name-only

# Commit
git add docs/infra/cloudflare-runtime-drift-sla.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-ownership-review-board.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-drift-exception-register.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-monthly-governance-evidence.md \
        docs/infra/cloudflare-drift-report.md \
        infra/cloudflare/README.md
git commit -m "docs(cloudflare): add runtime drift sla and review board"

# Push and open PR
git push origin fix/cloudflare-runtime-drift-sla-review-board
gh pr create --title "docs(cloudflare): add runtime drift sla and review board" \
  --body "Phase 15: Adds drift SLA classes, aging buckets, review board, exception register, and monthly governance evidence template. Read-only governance layer. No deploy. No secrets."
```

